            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1280171</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>如果有睇英超的球迷應該都知道，班霸曼城隨著傷兵累累，近期的走勢確實不太理想。不過今日的消息，相信會令不少曼城支持者感到興奮！曼城宣佈與運動品牌 PUMA 合作推出全新的生成式 AI 平台，讓全球球迷可以透過它設計具個人風格的球衣，設計後更可參加比賽，優勝者甚至會成為 2026/27 球季的第三球衣，確實十分吸引！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_002-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_002-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今次這個生成式 AI 球衣設計平台，是由 DEEPOBJECTS 開發，而在設計平台上，球迷只需要輸入電郵登記就可以獲得 16 個 credits，之後輸入球衣風格的關鍵字、球衣設計風格及球衣內含的顏色，再按下「Generate」就可以在半分鐘左右生成具個人風格的球衣，系統亦會有 4 款效果供用家進行微調，之後再遞交作品即可，用家亦可下載自己設計的球衣圖檔作收藏。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_003-694x516.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="516" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_003-694x516.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_003.jpg 1209w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_004-694x516.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="516" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_004-694x516.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_004.jpg 1211w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_005-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_005-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_005.jpg 1213w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280178" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_006-694x516.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="516" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_006-694x516.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_006.jpg 1211w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_008-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_008-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_008.jpg 1213w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_010-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_010-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_010.jpg 1209w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>筆者自己亦試過，如果快的話只需 5 分鐘已可遞交一份作品，而且整個過程十分流暢，即使沒有設計天分的筆者亦可設計出頗具型格的球衣。大家不妨自己試玩一下吧？萬一贏了隨時艾達臣、夏蘭特可能會穿著你設計的球衣在球場上馳騁呢！</p><p>來源：<a href="https://aicreator.puma.com/">曼城</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/12/10/mancity-puma-launched-genai-kit-design-platform/life-tech/">英超曼城推生成式 AI 球衣設計工具，舉行比賽優勝作品可成 26/27 球季第三球衣</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
