                <![CDATA[<p>近日中國深圳市寶安區首批擁有獨立路權的非機動車（港稱：電動可移動工具）示範道路正式完工，並已投入使用。這批示範道路有望為寶安電動可移動工具建立標準，為電動可移動工具駕駛者提供路權支援，提升騎行體驗和安全性。</p><p>示範道路包括新安六路、湖濱西路、寶民二路和沙松路等，新安六路設置了 1,000 米長的「非機動車道」，兩側各有 3 米寬的護欄隔離，保障騎行安全。湖濱西路壓縮機動車道後，新增 900 米長、2 米寬的「非機動車道」，緩解步行者和騎行者之間的衝突。寶民二路取消 54 個停車位，清理違停車輛後，設置 865 米長、2.5 米寬的「非機動車道」。沙松路將雙向 4 車道調整為雙向 2 車道，新增 1,500 米長、2.5 米寬的「非機動車道」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015030-694x577.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="577" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015030-694x577.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015030.jpg 982w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新安六路「非機動車道路」總長 1,000 米（圖片來源：<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">騰訊網</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280221" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded8310d-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded8310d-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded8310d.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造前的新安六路，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">寶安灣</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded6112a-694x408.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="408" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded6112a-694x408.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded6112a.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造後新安六路「非機動車道路」，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">寶安灣</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015230-684x580.jpg" alt="" width="684" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015230-684x580.jpg 684w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015230.jpg 976w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 684px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲湖濱西路「非機動車道路」總長 900 米（圖片來源：<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">騰訊網</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9deda0cf7-694x502.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="502" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9deda0cf7-694x502.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9deda0cf7.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造前的湖濱西路，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">寶安灣</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280224" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded92cfc-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded92cfc-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded92cfc.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造後湖濱西路「非機動車道路」，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">寶安灣</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015610-694x539.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="539" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015610-694x539.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015610.jpg 979w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲寶民二路「非機動車道路」總長 865 米（圖片來源：<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">騰訊網</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedc642a-694x520.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedc642a-694x520.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedc642a.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造前的寶民二路，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">寶安灣</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedb2155-694x389.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedb2155-694x389.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedb2155.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造後寶民二路「非機動車道路」，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">寶安灣</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280216" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015714-677x580.jpg" alt="" width="677" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015714-677x580.jpg 677w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015714.jpg 984w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 677px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲沙松路「非機動車道路」總長 1,500 米（圖片來源：<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">騰訊網</a>）</p><p>中國深圳市寶安區自 2019 年開始加快「非機動車道」建設，2024 年新增 40 公里獨立式「非機動車道」，以建立功能清晰、佈局合理、連續安全的舒適「非機動車道」網絡，減少電動可移動工具與城市交通系統的衝突，推動中國深圳市綠色出行和智慧城市發展。</p><p>除了增設「非機動車道」，中國深圳亦簡化了電動可移動工具「以舊換新」政策，目前無須再填寫大量表格，僅需辦理「報廢證明」即可換新電動可移動工具。另外中國深圳全部銷售商家（包括個體工商户）亦可銷售電動可移動工具，以方便中國深圳市民。</p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://www.sohu.com/a/833707215_121384220">搜狐</a>、<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">QQ News</a>、<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241205A00ZON00">QQ News</a></p><div class="html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1h91t0o xkh2ocl x78zum5 xdt5ytf x13a6bvl x193iq5w x1iyjqo2 x1eb86dx" role="presentation"></div><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========<br /><b>
